videos.description: Technical fouls and ejections are given to both South Carolina and Missouri after a loose ball in the second quarter leads to some pushing and shoving.
videos.headline: Tempers flare in South Carolina

videos.description: Sophie Cunningham drives and scores for Missouri to tie the game at 29-29 just before halftime.
videos.headline: Cunningham ties game before half

videos.description: Tyasha Harris takes the pass from Doniyah Cliney and knocks down a 3-pointer for the Gamecocks.
videos.headline: Harris hits wide-open 3

videos.description: Good passing by South Carolina ends with Alexis Jennings making a contested reverse layup.
videos.headline: Jennings gets friendly roll on tough layup
